<a class="right flag" rel="nofollow" id="flag_link542027" title="Flag this answer as inappropriate." href="/flagged/new?resource_id=542027&amp;resource_type=CommunityAnswer&amp;return_url=%2Fquestions%2F197654-if-this-wasn-t-supposed-to-be-a-murder%2Fanswers%2F542027-it-s-not-supposed-to">flag</a>
</div>
